      "title": "Nvidia calls China\u2019s DeepSeek R1 model \u2018an excellent AI advancement\u2019",
      "url": "https://www.cnbc.com/2025/01/27/nvidia-calls-chinas-deepseek-r1-model-an-excellent-ai-advancement.html",
